We’re Dressed for the Holidays
Old New York, Brighter Than Ever

The garlands are hung, the lights are glowing, and the villages are in motion — Pete’s Tavern is officially dressed for the season.
Inside, you’ll find everything that makes this time of year special: the glow of the bar, the warmth of familiar faces, and the comfort of good food shared together.

Small Group Reservations
Book Online

You can reserve a table for up to four guests through Resy
on our website.

Reservations for the

Holiday Season

Larger Parties
Contact Us

For parties of five or more, please email us directly at manager@petestavern.com.

We’ll get back to you shortly to confirm details.

A deposit ($50–$200) will be required for larger reservations. Please note that deposits are non-refundable.

Contact Us

Timing:
All reservations are for a maximum duration of two hours, so we can welcome as many guests as possible during this busy time.

Additional Details

Walk-Ins Welcome:

If you don’t see your preferred time, don’t worry — we do accept walk-ins.
The wait is usually no longer than 30 minutes. Add your name with the host, enjoy a drink at the bar, and soak in the holiday atmosphere while we prepare your table.

Outdoor Seating:

Our heated, decorated outdoor areas are also open and offered exclusively to walk-ins.

A Note About Drinks-Only Visits

During the holidays, we do our best to accommodate everyone who’d like to dine with us.
Because of the high demand for tables, we’re focusing our seated reservations on guests joining us for full meals.

If you’re just stopping by for a drink, we’d love to have you at the bar, where the spirit of the season is always flowing.
And of course — once the kitchen closes, all tables are available for drinks and late-night cheer.
